{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"fa16776b1c","title":"对章汉夫检讨的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"7ae5299f75","index":0,"year":1952,"month":9,"day":24,"articleId":"fa16776b1c"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"4f5ea05ebe","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"章汉夫，当时任中央人民政府外交部副部长。2]刘，指刘少奇。周，指周恩来。邓，指邓小平，当时任政务院副总理。"},{"id":"84dfb5532b","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指锡兰贸易代表团1952年9月22日向中国外交部提出的两点希望：一、希望中国政府将来派代表团去锡兰；二、希望代表团这次能会见毛泽东。"},{"id":"4ec1d83507","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"参见《关于较重要外交复文的送审问题的批语》一文。"}],"contents":[{"id":"61df5ac918","type":"title","text":"对章汉夫\"检讨的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c"},{"id":"4f5ea05ebe","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、周、邓、章汉夫同志阅，存周处。","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c"},{"id":"84dfb5532b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）锡兰代表所提两点，不应拒绝，具体安排请周总理处理。（二）章汉夫同志检讨尚好，这是第二次，仍不拟给予处分；如将来再犯，再议处分。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c"},{"id":"4ec1d83507","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c"},{"id":"54a60a3331","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五二年九月廿四日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c"}],"page":{"id":"986bac64da","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"fa16776b1c","start":260,"end":260}}}},"__N_SSG":true}